name: Ritual of Dark Magic
effect:
You can only activate this card if you control no monsters, except "Dark Magician", "Magician of Black Chaos", "Dark Magician Girl", or monsters that mention either of them in their text. For the rest of this turn, you cannot Normal or Special Summon monsters, except monsters with the same restriction.
Send 1 "Dark Magician" from your Deck to the GY; Special Summon up to 3 Ritual Monsters from your hand, Deck, or GY, ignoring their Summoning conditions. These monsters must either be named "Dark Magician", "Magician of Black Chaos", or specifically mention either in their text, and all must have different names. This is treated as a Ritual Summon.
If you Special Summon "Magician of Black Chaos" this way, it gains the following effect:
● Once per turn, when a card or effect is activated (Quick Effect): You can negate that effect, and if you do, banish that card.
You can only activate 1 "Ritual of Dark Magic" per turn.
